      <presentation id="LocalNetworkBlockedForUrls"><listBox refId="LocalNetworkBlockedForUrlsDesc">禁止網站向區域網路端點發出網路要求。</listBox></presentation>
      <presentation id="LoopbackNetworkAllowedForUrls"><listBox refId="LoopbackNetworkAllowedForUrlsDesc">允許網站向本機裝置發出網路要求。</listBox></presentation>
      <presentation id="LoopbackNetworkBlockedForUrls"><listBox refId="LoopbackNetworkBlockedForUrlsDesc">禁止網站向本機裝置發出網路要求。</listBox></presentation>
